{"tid":1172677,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【國際突發】秘魯北部發生8級地震 屬深層地震暫未有傷亡報告","createTime":"2019-05-26T14:58:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T19:54:17.000Z","uid":40010,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c56d2ba7acbba7b172f29586ba42a8df5be55a9b","tid":1172677,"uid":40010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T14:58:57.000Z","msg":"【國際突發】秘魯北部發生8級地震 屬深層地震暫未有傷亡報告<br />\n【新增內容】<br />\n美國地質勘探局（USGS）公佈，秘魯北部周日發生黎克特制8級地震。震央位於北部小鎮拉古納斯（Lagunas）東南75公里的亞馬遜叢林中，緊鄰巴西邊境，震源深度110公里，目前未有傷亡報告分。<br />\nUSGS指地震發生於當地凌晨2時40分，除巴西及秘魯兩國，鄰近的哥倫比亞及厄瓜多爾亦有震感。USGS指出「地震可能產生一些破壞，但僅於較小範圍」。<br />\n一些城市建築物倒塌及停電，接近震央的上亞馬遜省自來水供應亦受影響，秘魯總統比斯卡拉（Martin Vizcarra）在Twitter推文要求民眾保持鎮定，並表示政府正評估地震帶來的影響。<br />\n路透社/美聯社/法新社<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190526/59643535?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1jEPPOpJFXgod6JxRNjcsfHmHQr128TsPWUWI31xdtIZ83o2N7ZUvGXzY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190526%2F59643535%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1jEPPOpJFXgod6JxRNjcsfHmHQr128TsPWUWI31xdtIZ83o2N7ZUvGXzY&d=N%2B9SyAXHNe8JODsndO18BWyAt0yGCUsyxQooKadsmXE%3D&h=258b481a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190526%2F59643535%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1jEPPOpJFXgod6JxRNjcsfHmHQr128TsPWUWI31xdtIZ83o2N7ZUvGXzY&h=f94d4656\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190526/59643535?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1jEPPOpJFXgod6JxRNjcsfHmHQr128Ts